name: com.atsaetechnologies.defaulttools
description: This Unity editor tool automatically creates a default folder structure for your Unity project. With just one click, you can create top-level folders such as "Art", "Audio", "Code", "Documentation", "Plugins", "Prefabs", and "Scenes". It also creates subdirectories for each of these top-level folders. This is a great way to organize your Unity project and keep it clean.
